flowchart TD
  H[home-work] --> VS[vehicle-search]
  VS --> HC[Hold confirm<br/>Customer extension]
  HC --> TD[transport-default]
  TD --> OV[odometer-verified]
  OV --> ML[movement-transport-complete<br/>optional movement]
  ML --> FD[fueling-default]
  FD --> FU[fueling-unlocking]
  FU --> PT[fueling-pump-timeout<br/>~15s unlock expired]

  PT --> RY[Retry unlock]
  PT --> CP[Change pump]
  RY --> FU
  CP --> FD
